name: Technology transforms the world, and the world modifies us 2.0
description:
Nanotechnology, virtual reality, and the Internet Even if we don't need it, our lives are continuously being improved. A one-of-a-kind period of potential disasters in which, if we fail, everything would perish in hopeless darkness.

Moving on to a new stage, seeing new possibilities and wishing to reach them. Is this even conceivable without the 5th industrial revolution? Everyone should come up with their own solution.
